# 6. 心を守るために

Ena: <Mizuki! Any luck over there?>
Mizuki: No, there's too many people. I'm never gonna find her here.
Ena: <Okay... I didn't find her over here either.>
Ena: <I tried asking some Miya Girls students about her just now, but they said she's already gone home.>
Mizuki: Really...?
Mizuki: I'll check the diner just in case. There's a chance that she'll stop there before going home.
Ena: <Okay, thanks! I'll meet you there.>
Mizuki: Got it!
Mafuyu: (I really don't want to go home...)
Mafuyu: (I tried going to the diner... But I didn't see Kanade and the others there.)
Mafuyu: (Which is normal since it's not like we made plans to have an after-party there or anything...)
Mafuyu: What am I doing...?
Mafuyu: (I have that mock exam soon. I need to study for it.)
Mafuyu: (But...)
Mafuyu: (What am I supposed to tell her...?)
Mafuyu: (That I want to keep making music with my group?)
Mafuyu: (But she's never going to let me...)
Mafuyu: (Is there anything I can do at this point...?)
Mafuyu: Huh...?
Mafuyu: KAITO...
KAITO: <Now I get it. We couldn't reach you because your phone was broken...>
Mafuyu: H-How did you...?
KAITO: <Miku, try now.>
Miku's Voice: <Okay...>
Mafuyu: Miku...
Mafuyu: I was worried I'd never see you again...
Miku: <Mafuyu...>
KAITO: <Care to tell us what happened...?>
Mafuyu: So...
Mafuyu: My mom tried to take away my phone... I resisted and...
Mafuyu: It fell into my aquarium...
Miku: <Oh, I see...>
KAITO: <That explains it.>
KAITO: <Mafuyu... If you don't fight back now, this is probably going to be it for you.>
Mafuyu: What...?
KAITO: <I'm not just talking about being cut off from everyone. She's going to pick you apart clean.>
KAITO: <If you agree to do her bidding, she'll succeed in destroying who you are.>
KAITO: <You'll lose everything that you care about. For good.>
Mafuyu: ...!
Mafuyu: What am I supposed to do...?
KAITO: <Fight back. Tell her how you really feel.>
KAITO: <No one can predict what's going to happen, but this is the only option you have right now.>
Mafuyu: How I really feel...?
Mafuyu: But...
Mafuyu: If I do that, Mom will...
Miku: <If you tell her, she might get upset...>
Miku: <But if you don't say something, you might break...>
Miku: <I don't want that to happen... So, please, tell her.>
Miku: <We'll be here for you...>
Mafuyu: Miku...
Mafuyu: ...
Mafuyu: ...
Mafuyu: (But...)
Kanade: I won't go anywhere...
Mafuyu: Okay...
Mafuyu: I... I...
Mafuyu: I'll try telling her how I really feel.
